cast.overview: When an unexpected enemy emerges and threatens global safety and security, Nick Fury, director of the international peacekeeping agency known as S.H.I.E.L.D., finds himself in need of a team to pull the world back from the brink of disaster. Spanning the globe, a daring recruitment effort begins!
cast.title: The Avengers

details.biography: Layla Cushman is an American Actress born in Canton, OH. She grew up on a farm most of her life. Layla graduated from Malone University with a B.A. in Communications with an emphasis in media entertainment. She started her career as a TV host. After obtaining multiple agents, she soon started booking TV Commercials and eventually landed roles in both television and film. She continues to steadily add credits to her resume landing lead roles in her two latest projects, with many more to come.
details.name: Layla Cushman
